<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Tentang Kami - Sindika Platform</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .gradient-text {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #8b5cf6 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        
        .card-hover {
            transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        
        .card-hover:hover {
            transform: translateY(-12px) scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
        }
        
        .fade-in-up {
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out;
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        
        .slide-in {
            animation: slideIn 0.6s ease-out backwards;
        }
        
        @keyframes slideIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(-30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }
        
        .float {
            animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
        }
        
        .glow-on-hover:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
        }
        
        .stat-counter {
            animation: countUp 2s ease-out;
        }
        
        @keyframes countUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.5); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 via-blue-50/30 to-purple-50/30 text-slate-800 overflow-x-hidden">

    <!-- Animated Background -->
    <div class="fixed top-0 left-0 w-full h-full pointer-events-none overflow-hidden -z-10">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/3 w-[50rem] h-[50rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400/15 to-blue-600/15 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/3 w-[55rem] h-[55rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-400/15 to-pink-500/15 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 1s;"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-1/3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[40rem] h-[40rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-400/10 to-blue-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Header -->
      <%- include('partials/_navbar') %>


    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="w-full min-h-screen pt-40 pb-20 px-6">
        <section class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
            
            <!-- Hero Section -->
            <div class="text-center mb-20 fade-in-up">
                
                <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight leading-tight mb-6">
                    Pusat Komando untuk<br/>
                    <span class="gradient-text">Pelayanan Gereja Modern</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="mt-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-light">
                    Sindika adalah sebuah ekosistem digital end-to-end yang dirancang untuk secara fundamental mengubah cara gereja mengelola aset terpentingnya—data jemaat dan kegiatan—dengan menyatukan dua pilar utama:
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Two Pillars -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-20">
                <!-- Pillar 1 -->
                <div class="relative group slide-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/10 to-indigo-500/10 rounded-3xl blur-2xl group-hover:blur-3xl transition-all duration-500"></div>
                    <div class="relative card-hover p-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/95 to-white/80 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border border-white/60 h-full">
                        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-xl float">
                            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4">Manajemen Database Jemaat</h2>
                        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                            Berfungsi sebagai satu-satunya <span class="font-bold text-blue-600">"Buku Induk Digital"</span> yang akurat, mencatat semua data demografis, dari profil pribadi hingga struktur keluarga dan afiliasi rayon, memastikan data selalu terstruktur dan valid.
                        </p>
                        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Data Terpusat</span>
                            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Tervalidasi</span>
                            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-purple-50 text-purple-700 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Terstruktur</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Pillar 2 -->
                <div class="relative group slide-in" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500/10 to-pink-500/10 rounded-3xl blur-2xl group-hover:blur-3xl transition-all duration-500"></div>
                    <div class="relative card-hover p-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/95 to-white/80 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border border-white/60 h-full">
                        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-xl float" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
                            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4">Manajemen Kegiatan Efisien</h2>
                        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                            Mengelola seluruh siklus hidup acara, mulai dari perencanaan, pendaftaran online dengan validasi kuota, <span class="font-bold text-purple-600">absensi modern via QR Code</span>, hingga pengumpulan feedback untuk evaluasi.
                        </p>
                        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-purple-50 text-purple-700 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">End-to-End</span>
                            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-pink-50 text-pink-700 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">QR Code</span>
                            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-fuchsia-50 text-fuchsia-700 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Otomatis</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Integration Statement -->
            <div class="relative mb-20 fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.6s;">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500/5 via-purple-500/5 to-pink-500/5 rounded-3xl blur-2xl"></div>
                <div class="relative p-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/95 to-white/80 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border border-white/60 text-center glow-on-hover">
                    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                        <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 via-purple-500 to-pink-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-8 mx-auto shadow-2xl">
                            <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-4xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-6">Integrasi yang Powerful</h3>
                        <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
                            Dengan mengintegrasikan kedua pilar ini, Sindika dilengkapi dengan <span class="font-bold gradient-text">dashboard analitik canggih</span> yang mengubah data mentah menjadi wawasan strategis. Hasilnya adalah sebuah solusi terpadu yang memberdayakan gereja untuk <span class="font-bold text-blue-600">mengurangi beban administrasi</span> dan lebih fokus pada hal yang terpenting:
                        </p>
                        <div class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
                            <p class="text-3xl font-black text-white">Melayani Komunitas</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Stats Section -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-20">
                <div class="card-hover p-8 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/40 rounded-3xl shadow-xl text-center">
                    <div class="stat-counter text-5xl font-black gradient-text mb-3">70%</div>
                    <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Efisiensi Waktu</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Hemat waktu dalam pengelolaan data</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-hover p-8 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/40 rounded-3xl shadow-xl text-center" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
                    <div class="stat-counter text-5xl font-black gradient-text mb-3">100%</div>
                    <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Data Terintegrasi</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Sinkronisasi real-time penuh</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-hover p-8 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/40 rounded-3xl shadow-xl text-center" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
                    <div class="stat-counter text-5xl font-black gradient-text mb-3">24/7</div>
                    <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Akses Data</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Kapan saja, di mana saja</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Vision Section -->
            <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500/10 via-teal-500/10 to-cyan-500/10 rounded-3xl blur-2xl"></div>
                <div class="relative p-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/95 to-white/80 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border border-white/60">
                    <div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                        <div class="inline-block px-5 py-2 bg-emerald-100/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full text-emerald-700 font-semibold text-sm mb-6">
                             Visi Kami
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-4xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-6">Transformasi Digital Gereja Indonesia</h3>
                        <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
                            Kami percaya bahwa teknologi harus menjadi alat untuk memperkuat pelayanan, bukan memperumit. Sindika hadir untuk memberdayakan gereja-gereja di Indonesia dengan solusi digital yang sederhana, powerful, dan berorientasi pada pelayanan komunitas.
                        </p>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-left">
                            <div class="p-6 bg-emerald-50/50 rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100/50">
                                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
                                </div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Sederhana</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Interface intuitif yang mudah digunakan untuk semua kalangan</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="p-6 bg-teal-50/50 rounded-2xl border border-teal-100/50">
                                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-cyan-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
                                </div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Aman</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Keamanan data tingkat enterprise untuk melindungi informasi jemaat</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="p-6 bg-cyan-50/50 rounded-2xl border border-cyan-100/50">
                                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/></svg>
                                </div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Berorientasi Pelayanan</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Dirancang untuk membebaskan waktu agar lebih fokus melayani</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- CTA Section -->
            <div class="mt-20 text-center">
                <h3 class="text-4xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-6">Mulai Transformasi Digital Anda</h3>
                <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    Bergabunglah dengan gereja-gereja yang telah merasakan manfaat digitalisasi bersama Sindika
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
                    <a href="/jadwalkan-demo" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
                        </svg>
                        Diskusi dengan Kami
                    </a>
                    <a href="/solusi" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white text-slate-700 font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 border border-slate-200">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                        </svg>
                        Pelajari Solusi
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </section>
    </main>

     <%- include('partials/_footer') %> 
</body>
</html>